content: my favourite park in seoul 😭🤍 the best spot to see beautiful sunset!!!

Although it was only October to ride a bicycle in Hanjiang Park, it was still very cold to collect I SEOUL U (not this year), and later found that SEVENTEEN also went here to shoot a film. Check in in advance. XD traffic is also very convenient. It is just outside the subway station!
the best sunset spot in seoul, you'll get to see it with train on bridge 🌉 its so beautiful!
A great place for the residents of Gwangjin-gu!!! It's good to ride a bicycle and walk, and if you're hungry, you can eat ramen ㅎ
When Han River Citizen's Park comes, it's always healing~~! It's more romantic to go when the sunset is set
It's a great place to have a picnic :) After eating, be sure to clean up the trash!! 🤭🤭
The pride of Seoul Han River is just a good weather to go out
